<DOCNO> NYT19990619.0058 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-19 02:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1877 &Cx1f; tth-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-THIEL-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      06-19 0840
