<P>
   (BEGIN ITALICS HERE) I have some thoughts about education
reform.(END ITALICS HERE)
</P>
<P>
   An internship is a chance to occasionally run around and have
fun observing the spectacle without chafing against the confines of
a real job. . . . It can be the best of all worlds _ a share in the
action, but not an overwhelming stake in the future. This is not
