<P>
   INTERNATIONAL NEWS (``i'' category)
</P>
<P>
   US-RUSSIA (Cologne, Germany) _ President Clinton and leaders of
the world's most powerful industrialized democracies moved Saturday
to repair strained relations with Russia over the Balkans by prying
open their checkbooks to reward Russia's cooperation with the West
in Kosovo. By STEWART M. POWELL.
</P>
<P>
   Hearst News Service/Washington
